                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well, mem blur is fairly unreliable until you spend the 45 AA on Enhanced Forgetfulness. When it works, it works great.
<br />

<br />
But anyway, in your case the simplest thing would be to camp out and come back in...
<br />

<br />
Alternately, you could just keep the mob rooted. It would still be mad at you, but it wouldn't matter.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
