                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Option 2 - only works well if you have Ethereal Rune/LR5/spell haste and some decent mana/hps...
<br />

<br />
Slow the mob, apply cripple, then let your hasted/NDT pet beat on it while YOU hold aggro and chain rune yourself/nuke the mob.
<br />

<br />
Works surprisingly well on mobs in Bloodfields - just gotta be REALLY careful on the named mobs as they can chew thru Ethereal in 3-4 hits sometimes.
<br />

<br />
If it starts tearing you up too bad, apply mez and regroup.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
