                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Yakk wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">1> Boggle a bunch.  2 bogges per debuff spell.  Slow + mez + tash = 6 boggles.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
